// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1597 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 927e55fb-d752-5b56-b616-1d2073dcfed9

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:7*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*")
